Install Tails
=============

In this step, you will install Tails on a USB stick using
<span class="application">GNOME Disks</span>.

<div class="caution">

<p>All the data on this USB stick will be lost.</p>

</div>

1. Install <span class="application">GNOME Disks</span>.

   - If you are using the GNOME desktop environment,
     <span class="application">GNOME Disks</span> should be installed by
     default.

   - Otherwise, install the <span class="code">gnome-disk-utility</span>
     package using the usual installation method for your distribution.

